      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FITZROY NZ (4) came from one spot wider and raced parked for a resuming third at this circuit and distance last week. That was his first outing since winning here in November and he should be fitter for it. Yet to miss a place. Strong claims. SITTING ON EIGHT (5) was behind Fitzroy when he returned with a fourth last week. Ended last campaign in good form, recording two wins and a placing in the Sunshine Stars Yearling Sale Classic from his last three starts. Likely improver. JAMES ALFRED (2) has come from the second line in both starts since a spell and didn't miss by much last time. Draws well so could progress again. AMYLEE (3) was last seen at Group 1 level in August and won the rich APG Brisbane Sales Graduate 2F Final earlier in that campaign. Readied with a nice trial and draws well.",
